---
title: Goat's Cheese Fattoush
description: Fattoush is a salad of crunchy vegetables and toasted bread eaten all across the Middle East. Every family or restaurant will have their own and this is ours. It's usually made with pita bread but we've given things a twist by using ciabatta instead and added some goat's cheese for a tangy creaminess that contrasts beautifully with the cool, refreshing veg. It might not be traditional but it is delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/goat-s-cheese-fattoush-c30304cc.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/goat-s-cheese-fattoush-b1c44779.pdf
